    "title": "Mid-Level Fleet Manager at Gati",
    "description": "Join the Gati family as a Fleet Manager in Allahabad. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Gati:\nGati is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in KPI Monitoring\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in WMS\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Learning & development budget\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Allahabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Gati!",
